   "title": "Sixth Kalima Radd-e-Kufr",
   "arabic": "اللّٰهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ أَنْ أُشْرِكَ بِكَ شَيْئًا وَأَنَا أَعْلَمُ بِهِ، وَأَسْتَغْفِرُكَ لِمَا لَا أَعْلَمُ بِهِ، تُبْتُ عَنْهُ وَتَبَرَّأْتُ مِنَ الْكُفْرِ وَالشِّرْكِ وَالْكِذْبِ وَالْغِيبَةِ وَالْبِدْعَةِ وَالنَّمِيمَةِ وَالْفَوَاحِشِ وَالْبُهْتَانِ وَالْمَعَاصِي كُلِّهَا، وَأَسْلَمْتُ وَأَقُولُ لَا إِلٰهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ مُحَمَّدٌ رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ",
   "transliteration": "Allahumma inni a udhu bika min an ushrika bika shay-an wa ana alamu bih, wa astaghfiruka lima la alamu bih, tubtu anhu wa tabarra-tu minal-kufri wash-shirki wal-kidhbi wal-ghibati wal-bidati wan-namimati wal-fawahishi wal-buhtani wal-maasi kulliha, wa aslamtu wa aqulu la ilaha illallahu Muhammadur rasulullah.",
   "translation": "O Allah, refuge is sought in You from knowingly associating anything with You, and forgiveness is sought from You for what is not known. Repentance is made from it, and disavowal is made from disbelief, shirk, lying, backbiting, innovation, tale-bearing, indecency, slander, and all sins. Submission is made, and the declaration is: there is no deity except Allah, Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah.",
